        swl - - student willingness to learn (String)
        ds - - digital skills (String)
        sal - - student ability to learn (String)
        elm - - e-learning materials (String)
        iws - - instructor willingness to share(String)

        pu - - predicted usage (String)
        date - - date the survey was filled (String)
